719451f-c.folder: Houston Street (East) & Crosby Street, Manhattan, NY

724492f-a.text:
West Houston Street, south side, west from Crosby, to Mercer
Streets, after crossing Broadway. All these buildings were later razed (some are already in a state of demolition) to make way for the construction
of the Independent System Subway (Eighth Ave. subway).
September 19, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
